frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.subtitle2: Why are GSINTERNAME reviews different from other online reviews?
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.subtitle3: Are all customer reviews collected published?
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1: When looking for a trusted service center or dealership on the Internet,
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1-2: it is difficult to form an opinion on reliability and real satisfaction
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1-3: of their customers via Google, Facebook or Yellow Pages reviews:
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1-4: Too few, not very detailed, dissatisfied over-represented, false opinions...
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1-5: Thanks to GSINTERNAME customer reviews, the motorist now has a
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text1-6: a real benchmark of trust on the rooftop before going there.
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text2: After his/her visit in a dealership or service center, each customer is systematically
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text2-2: invited to share his opinion by answering a survey by email or SMS.
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text2-3: The GSINTERNAME customer review solution allows you to publish
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text2-4: authentic, unmodified, detailed and objective customer reviews
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text2-5: to help the motorist in his search for a trusted service center.
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text3: YES. GSINTERNAME referenced dealerships and service centers choose transparency
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text3-2: towards their customers and accept the automatic publication of all
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text3-3: their reviews on the Internet - whether positive or negative.
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text3-4: GSINTERNAME complies with the AFNOR NF Z74-501 standard
frontend:components:certificate:CtfModal.text3-5: which regulates the publication of online reviews.
